<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Augsburg</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Konrad Molitor, Bürger zu Nürnberg, wegen des Zolls für Nürnberger Bürger und Kaufleute entgegen altem Herkommen an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_107" id="52r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_107_r2l16">Augſpurg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_107_r2l18">Lieben frewnde / Als vvir <expan>ew
<del rend="strikethrough"><ex>r</ex></del></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_107_r2l17">
<del rend="strikethrough">weiſheit </del></ab></add> voꝛmals <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haben / vvie vns etliche </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_r2l19">vnſer <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd kaufleute fürbracht 
<del rend="strikethrough">haben </del> vnd cʒu vviſʒen getan haben / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_r2l20">vvie daʒ Jr von <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> wollen / beÿ ew ʒoll cʒu haben vnd cʒu <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> maÿnt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_r2l21">anders dann von <expan>alt<ex>er</ex></expan> herkomen ſeÿ etc 
<del rend="strikethrough">D </del>alʒo ſenden vvir cʒu ew <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_r2l22">Molitor vnſerm <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> mit ewch dauon cʒureden / vnd <expan>Rogam<ex>us</ex></expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_line_1574838549307_240">vvas <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> cʒu diſem male an ew vverb 
<del rend="strikethrough"> etc ein glaubbrief </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_107_line_1574838557979_245">
<del rend="strikethrough">in forma </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_107_line_1576678933554_13035">von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / das Jr </ab><ab facs="#facs_107_line_1576678936964_13040">Jm des glaubt / vnd lat </ab><ab facs="#facs_107_line_1576678940544_13045">vns des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_107_line_1576678943782_13050">wıder wiſʒen </ab></add> <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die <expan>Exaltat<ex>i</ex>on<ex>e</ex></expan> <expan>S<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>e</expan> <expan>Cruc<ex>is</ex></expan> Anno Octauo $ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_107" id="52r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Augspurg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieben frewnde, als wir <expan>ew</expan> vormals
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> haben, wie uns etliche
                        unser <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und kaufleute fürbracht und czu wiszen
                        getan haben, wie daz ir von <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> wollen bey ew zoll
                        czu haben und czu <expan>neme<ex>n</ex></expan> maynt, anders dann von
                                <expan>alt<ex>er</ex></expan> herkomen sey etc.; alzo senden wir czu
                        ew <expan>Conrad<ex>en</ex></expan> Molitor, unserm
                            <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, mit ewch davon czureden und
                                <expan>rogam<ex>us</ex></expan>, was <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> czu disem male an ew werb <add>von
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, das ir im des glaubt. Und lat uns des
                                    <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> wider wiszen</add>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
                                <expan>exaltat<ex>i</ex>on<ex>e</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>e</expan>
<expan>cruc<ex>is</ex></expan> anno octavo.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
